<figureCitation id="DA41D9941FAE0C1FA767A2438D2D69B5" captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figure 4. Holotype of Pyropia protolanceolata. Northeast side of Morro Rock, Morro Bay, California, USA, J. R. Hughey, 04 Apr 2012, UBC A 90634." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.52.5009.figure4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/45751" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
